I"½<h3 id="upload-firmware-with-tasmota-web-installer">Upload firmware with Tasmota web installer</h3>

<ol>
  <li>
    <p>Plug into the <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">USB</code> port of the board and check the port</p>

    <div class="language-sh highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code> <span class="nv">$ </span><span class="nb">ls</span> /dev/cu.<span class="k">*</span>

 /dev/cu.Bluetooth-Incoming-Port  /dev/cu.MINIJAMBOXbyJawbone  /dev/cu.SLAB_USBtoUART  /dev/cu.usbserial-1410
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Visit the <a href="https://tasmota.github.io/install/">Tasmota web installer</a> on the browser
 <a href="http://localhost:4000/assets/images/tutorials/blinky-tasmota-esp32c3-step-1.png"><img src="http://localhost:4000/assets/images/tutorials/blinky-tasmota-esp32c3-step-1.png" alt="" /></a></li>
  <li>Choose <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">ESP32-C3</code> in the dropdown list</li>
  <li>
    <p>Connect to the port e.g. <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">/dev/cu.SLAB_USBtoUART</code>
 <a href="http://localhost:4000/assets/images/tutorials/blinky-tasmota-esp32c3-step-2.png"><img src="http://localhost:4000/assets/images/tutorials/blinky-tasmota-esp32c3-step-2.png" alt="" /></a></p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Install Tasmota
 <a href="http://localhost:4000/assets/images/tutorials/blinky-tasmota-esp32c3-step-3.png"><img src="http://localhost:4000/assets/images/tutorials/blinky-tasmota-esp32c3-step-3.png" alt="" /></a></p>

    <p><a href="http://localhost:4000/assets/images/tutorials/blinky-tasmota-esp32c3-step-4.png"><img src="http://localhost:4000/assets/images/tutorials/blinky-tasmota-esp32c3-step-4.png" alt="" /></a></p>

    <p><a href="http://localhost:4000/assets/images/tutorials/blinky-tasmota-esp32c3-step-5.png"><img src="http://localhost:4000/assets/images/tutorials/blinky-tasmota-esp32c3-step-5.png" alt="" /></a></p>

    <p><a href="http://localhost:4000/assets/images/tutorials/blinky-tasmota-esp32c3-step-6.png"><img src="http://localhost:4000/assets/images/tutorials/blinky-tasmota-esp32c3-step-6.png" alt="" /></a></p>
  </li>
</ol>

<h3 id="connect-to-wifi-using-the-tasmota-web-installer">Connect to WiFi using the Tasmota web installer</h3>

<ol>
  <li>
    <p>Ensure automatic configure wifi dialogue is seen</p>

    <p><a href="http://localhost:4000/assets/images/tutorials/blinky-tasmota-esp32c3-wifi-step-1.png"><img src="http://localhost:4000/assets/images/tutorials/blinky-tasmota-esp32c3-wifi-step-1.png" alt="" /></a></p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Connect to the WiFi with SSID and password</p>

    <p><a href="http://localhost:4000/assets/images/tutorials/blinky-tasmota-esp32c3-wifi-step-2.png"><img src="http://localhost:4000/assets/images/tutorials/blinky-tasmota-esp32c3-wifi-step-2.png" alt="" /></a></p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Visit the device URL at <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">10.0.3.10</code></p>

    <p><a href="http://localhost:4000/assets/images/tutorials/blinky-tasmota-esp32c3-wifi-step-3.png"><img src="http://localhost:4000/assets/images/tutorials/blinky-tasmota-esp32c3-wifi-step-3.png" alt="" /></a></p>
  </li>
</ol>

<h3 id="control-led-via-the-web">Control LED via the web</h3>

<ol>
  <li>Wire up a simple LED to <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">GPIO3</code>
 <a href="http://localhost:4000/assets/images/tutorials/blinky-gpio3-esp32c3-schematic.png"><img src="http://localhost:4000/assets/images/tutorials/blinky-gpio3-esp32c3-schematic.png" alt="" /></a></li>
  <li>Plug in the board to an external power supply.</li>
  <li>Click <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Configuration</code>
 <a href="http://localhost:4000/assets/images/tutorials/blinky-tasmota-esp32c3-config.png"><img src="http://localhost:4000/assets/images/tutorials/blinky-tasmota-esp32c3-config.png" alt="" /></a></li>
  <li>Click <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Configure Module</code>
 <a href="http://localhost:4000/assets/images/tutorials/blinky-tasmota-esp32c3-config-module.png"><img src="http://localhost:4000/assets/images/tutorials/blinky-tasmota-esp32c3-config-module.png" alt="" /></a></li>
  <li>Change <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">GPIO3</code> to <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Relay</code> number 1 and save configuration
 <a href="http://localhost:4000/assets/images/tutorials/blinky-tasmota-esp32c3-relay.png"><img src="http://localhost:4000/assets/images/tutorials/blinky-tasmota-esp32c3-relay.png" alt="" /></a></li>
  <li>Go back to the main menu after device restart
 <a href="http://localhost:4000/assets/images/tutorials/blinky-tasmota-esp32c3-main.png"><img src="http://localhost:4000/assets/images/tutorials/blinky-tasmota-esp32c3-main.png" alt="" /></a></li>
  <li>Click the toggle <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">ON</code> and <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">OFF</code> to control the LED
 <a href="http://localhost:4000/assets/images/tutorials/blinky-tasmota-esp32c3-toggle.png"><img src="http://localhost:4000/assets/images/tutorials/blinky-tasmota-esp32c3-toggle.png" alt="" /></a></li>
</ol>

